          <title>DK Metcalf is leaving Seattle for Pittsburgh with a new deal in tow, AP sources say</title>
          <description><![CDATA[PITTSBURGH (AP) — The Pittsburgh Steelers finally have their established big-play wide receiver. The Seattle Seahawks are sending two-time Pro Bowler D.K. Metcalf to Pittsburgh for at least a second-round pick, sources with knowledge of the deal told The Associated Press on Sunday night.]]></description>
